summary: You were crossing the border of Skyrim when you were captured with the imperial legion! You are about to be executed, when i made this mod.
descriptionHtml:
This is a save game mod, so you need to have launched skyrim at least once, so lets get started.
<br />
<br />To install this mod, download it. (DUHH.) Open your (C:) Drive/Users/Tom/My Documents/My Games/Skyrim/Saves. And extract it into your Skyrim Folder.
author: SkyrimFan2233
